\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Positive values represent cation migration from terminal 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

 towards terminal 
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

, and vise-versa.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
It can be thought of as a variable proportional to the current length of
 the filament.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
A switch has two flux-linkage scales:
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{\mbox{crit}}$
\end_inset

 - 
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
Switching events occur when 
\begin_inset Formula $\left|\lambda\right|$
\end_inset

 passes 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{\mbox{crit}}$
\end_inset

.
 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
R=\begin{cases}
R_{\mbox{on}} & \lambda>\lambda_{\mbox{crit}}\\
R_{\mbox{off}} & \lambda<\lambda_{\mbox{crit}}
